OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA blustery and cool day with a
OL,6,Fmixture of sunshine and showers. The
OL,7,Fshowers heavy in places with a risk of
OL,8,Fhail and thunder, especially in the
OL,9,Feast. Showers also merging into bands
OL,10,Fto give some longer spells of rain.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cool and breezy evening
OL,13,Fwith further showers. Overnight some
OL,14,Finland areas becoming dry with lengthy
OL,15,Fclear spells developing here.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAnother day of sunshine and
OL,18,Fshowers, with the showers heavy and
OL,19,Fthundery in places. A more prolonged
OL,20,Fspell of rain possible for a time in
OL,21,Fthe west. Feeling cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
